comments: Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) makes marginal contact with Young (ATL) during his driving shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Reddish (ATL) and Allen (BKN) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Collins (ATL) sets the screen on Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on Young (ATL).
Irving (BKN) makes contact with Collins's (ATL) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bogdanovic (ATL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) and Collins (ATL) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Hunter (ATL) makes contact with the ball while defending Allen (BKN) after the rebound.
Durant (BKN) makes marginal contact with Young (ATL) during the drive,
Reddish (ATL) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
